<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA621_03_SU_0003_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    
    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />
    
    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema621_03.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema621_03_su_0003">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="1" lang="y">
          <div class="fraction_row">
            <div class="fraction_inn">
               바닷물로 만든 식수
              <span class="fraction_box"><span>7</span><span>9</span></span
              > L를 <span class="fraction_box"><span>2</span><span>9</span></span
              > L인 컵에 옮겨 담으려고 합니다. 식수를 모두 옮겨 담으면 몇 컵이 되는지 알아봅시다.
            </div>
            
          </div>
        </h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents paging_layout">
            <article class="page page_1">
              <div class="img_row">
                <div class="picture_wrap">
                  <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA621_03_SU/0003_content.png" alt="자치회 활동 이미지" />
                  <button class="zoom"></button>
                </div>
              
              <div class="input_area">
                <h3 lang="y">구하는 식을 써 보세요.</h3>
                <div class="question_box justify_center">
                  <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="(7)/(9)-:(2)/(9)"></math-field>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </article>
            <article class="page page_2">
              <h3 lang="y">
                식수를 모두 옮겨 담으면 몇 컵이 되는지 구하는 방법을 생각해 보고, 그림을 이용하여 알아보세요.
              </h3>
              <div class="speech_bubble">
                <div class="bubble_txt">
                  1컵의 반은<br>몇 컵일까?
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="question_box justify_center">
                <div class="box">
                  <div class="txt txt1">
                    <span class="fraction_box"><span>1</span><span>10</span></span>
                    <span lang="y">&nbsp;L</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="txt txt2" lang="y">1 (L)</div>
                  <div class="txt txt3" lang="y">0</div>
                  <div class="boolean_count_wrap col">
                    <button></button>
                    <button></button>
                    <button></button>
                    <button></button>
                  </div>
                  <span class="txt txt4" lang="y">1컵</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </article>
            <article class="page page_3">              
                <div class="img_row">
                  <div class="picture_wrap">
                    <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA621_03_SU/0003_content.png" alt="자치회 활동 이미지" />
                    <button class="zoom"></button>
                  </div>
                
                <div class="input_area">
                  <h3 lang="y">식수를 모두 옮겨 담으면 몇 컵이 되나요?</h3>
                  <div class="question_box justify_center">
                    <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="3(1)/(2)"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
            </article>
            

        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
          <!-- <button class="btnSubmit">확인</button> -->
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
